/*
ğŸ¯ OPTIONAL HOVER EFFECT
âš ï¸ DELETE IF NOT USED - Currently disabled by default

Adds elevation effect when hovering over cards.
To enable, uncomment the code below:

.moon-section__card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-0.5rem);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
}

Why disabled:
- Focus state already provides elevation
- Reduces visual noise for some users
- Can be distracting on touch devices

If you decide this effect is unwanted, DELETE THIS ENTIRE COMMENT BLOCK.
*/

